race.comment: AZABELLE (4) won well two back before a 2.6L victory last start over the mile at Pinjarra when sitting on the speed. This looks to shape similarly as she's drawn low and the claim of Nottle comes in handy. Can be up front in the run and bring up the hat-trick. LILLIAN (5) flew home first-up at Geraldton after a handy trial coming into this campaign. This is tougher, but she'll be better as she gets out over further and is Listed placed. CJP remains in the saddle and with the extra trip suiting, she'll can be right in the finish. MY HARV (7) won over this course and distance fresh before tackling Saturday grade most recently. Back to the scene of the crime third-up and she's open to further improvement. Drawn to get every chance and will be in this for a long way. TRESPASSING (9) is better than he showed last start and continues to find himself in strong form races. Include. GOLDEN KATHLEEN (1) can be flying late in the race.
